				<div class="post" id="post-825">

					<div class="author-box">
						<img src="http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/8aba67ae12e2ce3037e9154b5bf7185d?d=wavatar&amp;s=50" alt="" class="avatar user-2-avatar" width='50' height='50' />						<p>by <a href="http://blog.wessendorf.org/members/gerrit/" title="gerrit">gerrit</a></p>
